Tags:
  - Combat-Action=Work, Action and Society=On ‘Karma’ and ‘Karma Yoga’
By: Sri Ramana Maharshi
---
Devotee： Is society right in taking the life of a murderer?

Maharshi： What is it that prompted the murderer to commit the crime?
The same power awards him the punishment. Society or the State is only
a tool in the hands of the power.
